# Copy to app/.env and fill in. (app/.env đã gitignore)
# Firebase Web config — giá trị PUBLIC (bundle thẳng vào client JS).
# Lấy từ Firebase Console → Project Settings → Your apps → Web app.
# CI (deploy.yml) tách 4 key này từ Actions Variable `FIREBASE_WEB_CONFIG`.
VITE_FIREBASE_API_KEY=
VITE_FIREBASE_AUTH_DOMAIN=your-project.firebaseapp.com
VITE_FIREBASE_PROJECT_ID=hoc-cloud-cho-dev
VITE_FIREBASE_APP_ID=1:xxx:web:xxx

# Feature flag playground (optional, default bật). "false" = tắt mọi playground,
# fallback text-only. Runtime override per-URL: ?textMode=1.
VITE_ENABLE_DIAGRAM_PLAYGROUND=true
